**五房端「烏龍接駁站」：起初設置在五房村候車亭，之後移至烏龍村，位於[[台17線|台17線]]興龍路接沿海路上（近「[http://maps.google.com.tw/maps?q=%E5%B1%8F%E6%9D%B1%E7%B8%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%92%E9%84%89%E8%88%88%E9%BE%8D%E6%9D%91%E8%88%88%E9%BE%8D%E8%B7%AF 變電所][http://maps.google.com.tw/maps?q=%E5%B1%8F%E6%9D%B1%E7%B8%A3%E6%96%B0%E5%9C%92%E9%84%89%E8%88%88%E9%BE%8D%E6%9D%91%E8%88%88%E9%BE%8D%E8%B7%AF&ie=UTF8&ll=22.492029,120.457106&spn=0.008505,0.013937&t=h&z=17&vpsrc=6&brcurrent=3,0x3471e1ba8fb125f9:0x901783a86f3d1f46,0,0x3471d94ee1742281:0xed215194b3a68355&layer=c&cbll=22.492065,120.456969&panoid=Gq9lUNI_8x2Z2IUUt-J_3w&cbp=12,13.57,,0,-3.06 （街景）]」）
